column5: Description
Sends a wave of ice out in a circle, Freezing all enemies within 50 units
Forms a volcano that erupts molten projectiles, sinking back into the earth after 20 seconds
Launches hooks at all enemies within 60 units, stunning them and pulling them in
Revives all Ancestral Totems within 50 units
Revives the nearest Ancestral Totem
Bursts healing pulses in a circle for 20 seconds
Fully heals all Teammates
Drains the Life from nearby Enemy Corpses, preventing them from respawning for 10 seconds
Encases all enemies within 50 units in jade for 10 seconds
Buffs all Teammates within 60 units for 20 seconds, making them invulnerable to damage and unable to be interrupted when banishing totems
Constructs a very long wall
Casts a Tidal Wave which rolls forwards, crashing on the first Enemy it hits
Charges a beam of lightning, unleashing it after a short time. This beam can shock Enemies.
Pulls all Teammate totems within 40 units inwards
Provides more Attack Damage to all Teammates in an area
Provides more Spell Damage to all Teammates in an area
Creates shocked ground in a radius of 60 for 30 seconds.
Repeatedly Stuns all enemies in within 40 units for 20 seconds
All Ancestral Totems within 60 units are immune to banishing for 20 seconds
Adds a buff to all Teammates that creates a highly damaging explosion of fire when they die
Returns all Teammates to a location near their Ancestral Totems
Creates a proximity shield for 20 seconds
Removes all ailments from Teammates within 60 units and gives them ailment immunity for 20 seconds
Summons multiple stampedes of spiritual boars that charge forwards
All Teammates leech 100% of damage they deal as life to their Ancestral Totems for 20 seconds
All enemies within 60 units banish totems at a slower rate for 30 seconds
Creates a whirlwind of air that moves forward, giving all Teammates inside it Tailwind
